    "description": {
      "value": "<p><strong>Harmony Flute (Fetish)</strong></p><p><em>Creation Cost: 5 Gnosis.</em></p><p><strong>Effect:</strong> As an action, play the flute. One hostile creature within 30 feet must make a Wisdom saving throw or be charmed by you until the end of its next turn. While charmed this way, the creature cannot take hostile actions.</p><p>This effect may be used <strong>once per long rest</strong>.</p><p><strong>Fetish Rating:</strong> 1. <strong>Minimum Max Gnosis:</strong> 3. Cannot use while raging unless this fetish states otherwise. Spirit Attention: you can have a number of actively empowered fetishes equal to your Wisdom modifier (minimum 1); instantaneous effects do not count after resolution.</p><p><code>[GAROU_FETISH] id=harmony-flute; rating=1; minGnosis=3; activation=action</code></p>",
